text:

text:
Aur alan bhai, tera first impression padhaku me tha... baad me pata chal tere jaisa chill and multitasking banda kam hi hai. drams se acads tak sabme phod deta tha. Maal ka baat mat karo tum, wo to ham passively le hi rhe the tere room ke bagal me rehne ke karan bas formality bachi thiğŸ˜‚.

text:
Aur bhai acads god. Tere jaisa  dedicated, hard working and goal oriented banda nhi dekhe. Crypto jaise courses me doubts clear karne ke liye shukriya. Kisi ko aata ya na aata ho itna bharosa tha tumko jarur pata hoga.
Aur manali trip to yaad hi rehega apna. Kafi masti kiye wahan.. bas harbaar car me thoos ke baithne me kachumar nikal jaata thağŸ˜‚.

author: Harshit  Kumar

text:
Aur bhai archies, tere sath bhi bahut bulla kate hai kabhi snehan ke room pe to kabhi tere aur mere. 
Exam ke ek din pehle ka apna topic discussion bhi mast hota tha . Networks ke assign ke liye raat me jagkar hamlog ka help karne ke liye shukriya. waise chahe agle din assignment deadline hi kyo na ho, tumhara raat me 12 bje sona wala habit alag hai bhai. jab bhi subah uthna jaruri hota tha tumko ek baar batana jaruri hogya tha. kabhi kabhar breakfast time pe apan mil jate the bas antar yhi ki tum soke utha hota thağŸ˜‚. Aur last sem me volleyball khelne me maja aaya sabke sath. 
Manali trip wala experience bhi epic tha. usme sabse jada maja bungee jumping karne me aaya tha. sabka reaction alag alag thağŸ˜†. Waise, ab aage kya karne ka socha hai rocket banana ya music bandğŸ˜„ ? Milte hai ab bangalore me, bas ye pata lagana hai ki sabka company ek dusre se kitna door hai.
author: Harshit  Kumar

text:
Aur saini bhai, kya haal chaal. One of the most funny guy i have met other than raju. tere se baat karne me alag hi maja aata tha... pata nhi kya kya cringy bakwas karte rehta thağŸ˜‚... I can say that you and raju are on same level but have different genre of talkingğŸ˜†.
ek baar jo hamlog ka mehfil jamta tha kisi ke room pe to wo khatam hone ka naam hi nhi leta tha. Kafi kheecha tani kiye hai ekdusre ka mini militia khelte time. Roj hi din ka hogya tha apna. Aur tera drawing mast hai bhai. Aisa lagta hai ki mini militia ke characters me jaan daal diye ho. Baaki last sem me aate to thora aur khel lete sath me.
Agey touch me rehna.
author: Harshit  Kumar

text:
Aur tanmay bhai tere sath manali trip kaise bhul sakte hai, saara planning and funding ka bhar tere upar tha. mountain climbing me adhe dur ke baad tumko company dena para thağŸ˜„ (waise thak to ham bhi gye the uss samay). Hamlogo ka TA project wala din to yaad hi hai, pta nhi kya kya karna para tha usmeğŸ˜‚. Aur kai cs ke assignments ko sath me discuss karne ke liye thanks. Jab bhi kuch assignment related doubt hota tha tumse baat karne ke baad kuch na kuch solution to nikal hi ata tha. Aur han agey bhi plan karte hai koi trip.
Baaki bangalore me milte hai.
author: Harshit  Kumar

text:
Aur first year room partner, and more than that bhai. Tumhara room was like hamara room kabhi bhi aake aaraam karna.First year se last year tak sath hi rahey hai. Mini militia khlene ke bahane kafi masti kiye hai. Last sem me sath me volleyball khelna, room pe chill marke projector pe movies dekhna aur wall pe hamara aur raju ka drawing to yaad hi rehega. Concentration to tera alag level ka hai, kaan ke pas chillana parta tha kuch bolna ho to. 
Agey milte hai bangalore me jab corona kam ho, sath hi rehenge aspas.
author: Harshit  Kumar

text:
Aur nimish bhai, tere bina to college life acche se explain nhi kiya jaa sakta. First year me roj din sath me library and cc jaake esc101 and other courses ke lectures padhna, mini militia me tera consistent last aane ka record, 2nd year ke summer me sath me projects and intern prep karna and apna offcampus intern jo finally intern me convert nhi ho paya ğŸ˜… kaise bhul sakte hai. Summer me to apna har week ka ek baar pizza hogya tha ğŸ˜„. Koi bhi cheez kar rhe ho apan ek dusre ko ek na ekbaar puch hi lete the sath karne ke liye. Last sem ka masti to alag hua kuch hi din ka tha but best tha. Aur han bhai jaise tum advice dete rehta hai kai cheezo pe wo agey bi dete rehna.
Bas yhi dukh hai ki apna crypto ka paisa kab recover hoga?
Agey milte hai bangalore me, aspas hi rehenge.
author: Harshit  Kumar

text:
Bhai tere sath to bahut masti kiye hain first se last year tak. Assignment, project aur bhi kahi sare cheez to sath me kiye hai. Mini militia, sometime Pubg, aur snehan ke room pe roj din ka bulla katna. Tu jo bolta tha usme se adhi cheeze to tum aise hi man se bana dete the, par ussi ko leke agey bakwas chalta rehta tha hamara ğŸ˜‚. Aur tumko uthana was like deewar pe pathar maarna. Aise hi agey bangalore me bhi milke baatey karte hai. 
Aur haan mere room pe jo likha hai wo yaad hai na  "kon kiska beta hai"ğŸ˜‚.

text:

Agey DM banoge to hamare pe kripa barsaye rakhna ğŸ˜.

Waise tere room pe random bakwas kisi cheez pe karne me maja aata tha.Speaker pe songs kon chalayega ğŸ˜‚, kon kiska beta haiğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜†, raju ki maarna sath me . text:
